{"tid":141416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人貨車蘭桂坊衝20米撞途人","createTime":"2017-03-03T02:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T14:38:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ca915e0a1a033a76787c1be41e6dd18ce201cf","tid":141416,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:01:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19945712&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19945712%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170303&d=vE0XmFSztYUmu7sR0UJCJPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=dad89492\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19945712%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170303&h=6c3525a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19945712&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170303</a><br />\n<br />\n無人貨車蘭桂坊衝20米撞途人<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中環蘭桂坊昨發生驚險車禍，一輛停在德己立街的密斗貨車，突然在無人駕駛下沿斜路溜前，俯衝20米先後撞倒途人及一輛貨車，最後撼欄杆始停下。一名途人被碎片濺中輕傷，另一男子則被撞傷送院治理，警方已展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n密斗貨車由斜路俯衝撞向欄杆停下。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n司機聲稱有拉手掣<br />\n<br />\n涉事南亞裔司機Ahmed（48歲），昨晨11時許駕駛密斗貨車停在德己立街與和安里交界，之後與跟車工人下車落貨，其間貨車突溜前並沿斜路俯衝；62歲姓莫男子剛橫過馬路，當場被撞倒受傷，貨車繼續衝行再撞向一輛準備轉入威靈頓街的客貨車，最後撞向鐵欄停下，在欄杆附近的48歲姓馬男子被碎片擊中受傷。肇事貨車前後俯衝約20米。<br />\n救護員到場為傷者治理，其中馬經敷治後毋須送院，莫則額頭及膝蓋擦傷，由救護車送院治理。警方在場調查，肇事司機Ahmed報稱有拉好手掣，懷疑是機件故障肇禍。另一被撞客貨車的49歲姓譚司機稱，當時他駕車沿德己立街落斜，停在路口準備轉入威靈頓街。<br />\n目擊者溫先生說：「如果冇撞欄就撞報紙檔，直衝皇后大道中呀！我自己行遲一步都中（被撞）。」在場86歲的女報販彩姐則說：「突然嘭一聲&hellip;&hellip;全靠嗰幾條鐵（欄杆）救我囉，唔係就死梗。」彩姐十幾歲開始在該處開檔，「由兩個仙一份報紙，賣到𠵱家」。<br />\n另一名姓王報販稱，事發時他正準備開檔，現場很多途人：「砰砰嘭嘭&hellip;&hellip;有人大嗌，力度好大！」他指幾年前都有同類車禍發生。<br />\n■記者劉柏麟"},{"pid":"7aa4a2b58b79ba0515d83be37ca5c0280d243f09","tid":141416,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"南亞裔司機Ahmed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9551facf5585e964acb8d14b54bd3eacfa6e0ea6","tid":141416,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"係咪恐怖襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bdfc1446a1d5716b8422e06e2a92b94e596d28","tid":141416,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f3479fb63bbb44e8a27a756ea0ebd746a8ed660","tid":141416,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:27:30.000Z","msg":"又係南亞人"},{"pid":"316e5c765e3374ac6763f3443c9d6e30dc7cc674","tid":141416,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:39:44.000Z","msg":"allahu akbar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9473baa7fcb4f5c190f63c2162c00f33cebf18cd","tid":141416,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:39:56.000Z","msg":"涉事南亞裔司機  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd2d511f527e8cc24d3ced7e4ccc24a9704755a","tid":141416,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:34:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阿拉鴨巴</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4de0872f009dfe1833481d421c866596054b361","tid":141416,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}